What do we do with it? Let's use positive psychology.
该怎么应对呢 让我们应用积极心理学

1033
01:06:22,980 --> 01:06:24,760
Because it really is a problem that
因为这确实是我们希望

1034
01:06:24,990 --> 01:06:26,750
we want to be able to deal with,
