1035
01:06:26,980 --> 01:06:28,610
that I know,certainly,personally,
至少我个人

1036
01:06:28,820 --> 01:06:31,130
it's a problem that I dealt with for very long time.
很早就想解决它了

1037
01:06:31,850 --> 01:06:34,010
So the conventional question,
传统的问题

1038
01:06:34,220 --> 01:06:36,470
the traditional psychologist question was
传统的心理学家会问

1039
01:06:37,520 --> 01:06:39,330
"why are so many people stressed?"
"为什么这么多人压力过大"

1040
01:06:39,580 --> 01:06:41,900
An important question,good question,
这是非常重要的 非常好的问题

1041
01:06:42,160 --> 01:06:47,490
question that yielded many great answers but not enough.
能够引出很多好的回答 但仍然不够

1042
01:06:47,820 --> 01:06:49,790
And then positive psychologists came in.
然后积极心理学出现了

1043
01:06:50,030 --> 01:06:56,610
And what they did was ask also the positive question.
而他们所做的是 同样问一些积极地问题

1044
01:06:56,870 --> 01:06:57,770
Just like
就像

1045
