"The Power of Full Engagement"-
《精力管理》

1133
01:11:56,630 --> 01:11:58,910
that again,I highly recommend you read.
我非常推荐你们读这本书

1134
01:11:59,130 --> 01:12:00,740
Maybe over your spring break.
也许在春假时你们可以读一读

1135
01:12:01,520 --> 01:12:04,570
And what Tony Schwartz and Jim Loehr talk about,
Tony Schwartz和Jim Loehr想说的是

1136
01:12:04,820 --> 01:12:08,620
is that what we need to do is change our perception of our day
我们所要做的是将我们对生活的理解

1137
01:12:08,900 --> 01:12:13,380
from being marathon runners to being sprinters,
从马拉松运动员变为短跑运动员

1138
01:12:15,120 --> 01:12:18,190
from going on and on and on
从不停地跑 跑 跑

1139
01:12:18,510 --> 01:12:23,350
to sprinting,recovery,sprinting,recovery.
变为短跑 恢复 短跑 恢复

1140
01:12:23,590 --> 01:12:28,660
That understanding,that understanding changed my life.
这个想法 这个想法改变了我的人生

1141
01:12:32,350 --> 01:12:37,390
I was a marathon runner,metaphorically- meaning at work.
我曾经是个马拉松运动员 我是指在工作上

1142
01:12:37,630 --> 01:12:39,040
I used to work 14 hours a day.
我每天工作14个小时

1143
