I loved my work.I worked extremely hard.
我热爱我的工作 非常努力

1144
01:12:41,600 --> 01:12:47,030
And then I decided to get married and to have children.
然后我决定结婚生子

1145
01:12:47,250 --> 01:12:50,250
And I knew that things would change as a result of that.
我知道因此可能一切会变得不一样

1146
01:12:50,990 --> 01:12:53,780
And I said,"OK.I have to compromise.
我说"好吧 我必须妥协

